skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: rambling wreck
des: This still will share facts about Georgia Tech traditions. Information included in this skill can be found at http://www.gatech.edu/about/history-and-traditions and http://traditions.gatech.edu/. Mild profanity may be used. Users can ask “What’s the good word?” “How about ‘em dawgs?” or “Tell me a fact.”
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
